data.description: This is a nearly new home located on Sayre Golf Course. Home offers 4 bedrooms that are all spacious with good size closets, master bedroom offers 2 closets, double vanities and great storage. Dining room has french door leading to the patio facing the golf course giving your great views. In addition there is a storm shelter and storage shed. This home is a must see and priced to sell!
